g.title: j123603385
g.text: Everything you've told me of the future...

g.title: j1233267895
g.text: Entrati.

g.title: j635389332
g.text: The Man in the Wall.

g.title: j4246568066
g.text: The Sentients.

g.title: j112216932
g.text: Tau.

g.title: j1210949673
g.text: Someday - and someday soon, I feel like the future will need you.

g.title: j4018610394
g.text: What're you trying to say?

g.title: j3118344970
g.text: I gtg. [End.]

g.title: j983807031
g.text: I'm saying that sooner or later, you're going to go home and leave us here.

g.title: j648438371
g.text: Are you telling me to leave?

g.title: j1373702874
g.text: No. I'm saying that I feel like it's inevitable. Someday you *will* leave.

g.title: j3303785408
g.text: Travel isn't permanent. I can come and go.

g.title: j1133837357
g.text: Screw the future. I never belonged there.

g.title: j3211096068
g.text: Right. And someday you'll walk through that portal and never come back.

g.title: j3590182472
g.text: Are you telling me that if "The Lotus" came calling, you wouldn't go running?

g.title: j3936646246
g.text: Why're you so angry with me for no reason?

g.title: j1472885639
g.text: Says who?

g.title: j4046287588
g.text: You wouldn't charge off to save the universe again?

g.title: j4050026082
g.text: This is a valid concern.

g.title: j1414264172
g.text: Says common sense.

g.title: j4177767620
g.text: The future's in good hands. They don't need me. This place does.

g.title: j2629683767
g.text: I...yeah. I'm sorry. I'd have to go, if the universe was at stake.

g.title: j3557277668
g.text: Either you get sick of us and leave, or something horrible happens.

g.title: j429247799
g.text: Common sense? Or fear?

g.title: j4187651945
g.text: This is asinine. [End.]

g.title: j3639738292
g.text: I don't want to leave, Arthur.

g.title: j352578777
g.text: We need your help with what? Viktor Vodiyanoi? Please.

g.title: j67720314
g.text: Honesty. Thank you.

g.title: j506509865
g.text: Something horrible?

g.title: j1297942182
g.text: Thanks for the vote of confidence...

g.title: j4260326070
g.text: I repeat: Why are you angry at me for no reason?

g.title: j2154527059
g.text: I'm not afraid. I was fine before you. I'll be fine after you.

g.title: j955137010
g.text: So why are you pushing me away?

g.title: j191839750
g.text: I've seen what the future's up against.

g.title: j410800169
g.text: Would you come back?

g.title: j1723177529
g.text: You might die in the future, and I'd...never know.

g.title: j2031972721
g.text: I'm being serious.

g.title: j2553037471
g.text: So, what's the problem, exactly?

g.title: j2272466153
g.text: Hey look on the bright side, you'll be the best Excalibur again if I go.

g.title: j1868067829
g.text: I'm not.

g.title: j1479330743
g.text: I can handle some Techrot and some overzealous military goons.

g.title: j3761252153
g.text: I would fight tooth and nail to make it back to you.

g.title: j3066518587
g.text: Meh.

g.title: j4218740931
g.text: I just...I have this recurring nightmare of you...

g.title: j924560125
g.text: No, you're not. You're looking for an excuse.

g.title: j4168458559
g.text: I'm not having an argument with you over something that isn't real. [End.]

g.title: j1875355931
g.text: Since I clearly don't matter to you.

g.title: j144616954
g.text: Oh, *sod off.*

g.title: j316994734
g.text: LOL

g.title: j2912857069
g.text: Then what the *hell* do you call this?

g.title: j256690688
g.text: Fine. Then the truth is? Ironically, I can't predict the future.

g.title: j1051971256
g.text: I don't want to leave. So what do you want me to say?

g.title: j3990250739
g.text: My home is here, with you.

g.title: j4156401910
g.text: Boolean ArthurDating is now false.

g.title: j1719233482
g.text: Laying in a puddle of blood on some distant planet, killed by some...alien robot, or mutated...whatever.

g.title: j3100275110
g.text: You want a reason to push me away. You want a reason to not have to *care.*

g.title: j3167795900
g.text: That's not what I meant.

g.title: j3226526154
g.text: I'm being serious.

g.title: j2490864122
g.text: This is called an adult conversation.

g.title: j2539424122
g.text: Then I'll ask again. If you get pulled away: would you come back?

g.title: j3247277522
g.text: I don't know.

g.title: j4062609033
g.text: But you're a soldier, like me. And sometimes soldiers don't come home.

g.title: j2266979906
g.text: Boolean ArthurNoDate is now true.

g.title: j2841282438
g.text: And I wouldn't have been there to save you.

g.title: j4210254394
g.text: People die. People disappear. That's called *life.*

g.title: j2286707919
g.text: Do you want me to leave? Or stay?

g.title: j790682823
g.text: What *did* you mean?

g.title: j1681271532
g.text: You could disappear at any time. You could get sick of us or die. And I'd never know.

g.title: j2592468570
g.text: No, this is called you looking for excuses.

g.title: j102993562
g.text: I don't have any plans to leave. And that's the best I can do right now.

g.title: j4123920702
g.text: After this conversation? I'm thinking not.

g.title: j1560543600
g.text: If I could, of course. Why would you assume otherwise?

g.title: j1797352607
g.text: All right, let's start over. Can you tell me what's really bothering you?

g.title: j654147558
g.text: Well, let me know when you figure it out. I'm done with this conversation. [End.]

g.title: j497519137
g.text: Yeah. And that's just...how it goes, sometimes.

g.title: j2057575670
g.text: The good news is, I'm really hard to kill.

g.title: j1584966575
g.text: Boolean IsDating is now false.

g.title: j3027442400
g.text: And before you claim "I promise I won't go," you're lying.

g.title: j200883710
g.text: It happens to anyone, at any time. Nothing is ever certain.

g.title: j3763807298
g.text: I want you to stay.

g.title: j578120966
g.text: First thing's first. You matter to me.

g.title: j2008653579
g.text: Stop looking for excuses.

g.title: j1664651796
g.text: So do you want me to stay? Or leave?

g.title: j2418114750
g.text: You don't want to get hurt, and I understand that. I respect that.

g.title: j568169663
g.text: And that's supposed to be enough?

g.title: j2792948767
g.text: Boolean ArthurDating is now false.

g.title: j799839981
g.text: Too much time expecting the worst of people.

g.title: j1998630647
g.text: I just keep...having this nightmare, where you're gone.

g.title: j2337114876
g.text: I'll hold onto the dream of retirement.

g.title: j333068118
g.text: Heh. Yeah. I know.

g.title: j1240040832
g.text: Well. Better to find out this was a mistake *now* rather than *later.* I'm ending this between us.

g.title: j2836096577
g.text: Because I know you. And I know if you get that call, you're going. You'll do the right thing.

g.title: j1227576267
g.text: Whether or not they're freaks or from the future or not.

g.title: j2680149271
g.text: And I'm...worried someday you'll leave and...never come back.

g.title: j4146249401
g.text: Yeah. And it should be enough.

g.title: j674369225
g.text: I...don't know.

g.title: j2608555659
g.text: But people disappear all the time. Normal people.

g.title: j247675240
g.text: Boolean ArthurNoDate is now true.

g.title: j1599307598
g.text: I'm jumping at shadows.

g.title: j3034954526
g.text: Where I couldn't save you.

g.title: j2488057436
g.text: I suppose it's hard to ever know how much time we have.

g.title: j577835638
g.text: That's who you are.

g.title: j1131334524
g.text: So stop making *excuses* and tell me what's *really* bothering you, Arthur.

g.title: j1600359982
g.text: Because I might be from the future, but I can't predict it, Arthur.

g.title: j3508408668
g.text: I think you don't want to get hurt.

g.title: j91453885
g.text: Let me know when you figure it out. [End.]

g.title: j870938419
g.text: People die all the time. Normal people.

g.title: j3698536617
g.text: Boolean IsDating is now false.

g.title: j4101369764
g.text: And... I can't stand the thought of it.

g.title: j3176263061
g.text: +20 Chemistry

g.title: j1439226521
g.text: But the idea of it doesn't scare me. I'm not lying about that.

g.title: j1522206925
g.text: I don't know what the future holds for us.

g.title: j605065966
g.text: Can you blame me?

g.title: j3616613686
g.text: You don't have to be a freak or from the future for that to happen.

g.title: j145344513
g.text: Well, better we end this now, rather than later, I suppose.

g.title: j406671669
g.text: I...don't think anybody's ever worried about *me* before.

g.title: j2983169786
g.text: Remember, *I'm* the better fighter, here. I don't need saving.

g.title: j2927835825
g.text: Best to just...cherish what we've got.

g.title: j4277444504
g.text: Because whatever the thought of you dying does to me, it's somehow far, far worse than that.

g.title: j1777069734
g.text: But right now? I want to be here with you.

g.title: j520393401
g.text: Of course not.

g.title: j3842359883
g.text: That doesn't mean I'm going to intentionally disappear.

g.title: j3779064716
g.text: So stop searching for reasons to push me away.

g.title: j2346733335
g.text: That might be the...sweetest thing I've ever heard.

g.title: j3831869649
g.text: Yeah. Screw me for caring.

g.title: j3175322152
g.text: I don't even know if it has a name.

g.title: j136595195
g.text: But I think you need to figure out if you're okay with this relationship.

g.title: j1327115764
g.text: Intentionally.

g.title: j22131974
g.text: If you want this to end, just end it. Don't blame it on me someday "disappearing."

g.title: j1949531489
g.text: Not that you're worried about me--I don't want that.

g.title: j621642916
g.text: Then I vow I will always fight tooth and nail to come back to you.

g.title: j3536117032
g.text: I...don't know what to say.

g.title: j1987146739
g.text: I can't do this to you. I can't. We need to end this now. [Break up with Arthur.]

g.title: j1320648692
g.text: Because yeah. Someday, something MIGHT happen.

g.title: j1361849668
g.text: Something might happen. I can't promise otherwise.

g.title: j924071328
g.text: No...sorry.

g.title: j2463313
g.text: But that you *care.*

g.title: j4266347191
g.text: That's the most I can ask for. And maybe take me with you if you ever find a way.

g.title: j3882333887
g.text: Just tell me you'll try not to die out there. Or at least take me with you if you ever find a way.

g.title: j2800685685
g.text: Boolean ArthurDating is now false.

g.title: j412925101
g.text: That's called life.

g.title: j1973579465
g.text: You're right.

g.title: j2517830963
g.text: I can't promise I'll always make it back alive.

g.title: j84892540
g.text: I promise.

g.title: j778417404
g.text: Boolean IsDating is now false.

g.title: j1648034000
g.text: Sometimes, people don't come back.

g.title: j2238753299
g.text: I don't deal well when I'm the one trapped in the past and you're the one rushing off into battle to save the world.

g.title: j3306326987
g.text: But I can promise I'll fight tooth and nail every single time to do so.

g.title: j367054140
g.text: +20 Chemistry

g.title: j1575498919
g.text: Boolean ArthurNoDate is now true.

g.title: j2514074651
g.text: No kidding.

g.title: j2518288732
g.text: I'd feel the same in your shoes.

g.title: j3509217217
g.text: +20 Chemistry

g.title: j392965981
g.text: I...yeah. You're right. This is for the best.

g.title: j1432885890
g.text: That's the most a soldier - and a man - can ask for. Thanks, sweets.
